name: The Boys
p: A group of vigilantes set out to take down corrupt superheroes who abuse their superpowers.

name: The Big Bang Theory
p: A woman who moves into an apartment across the hall from two brilliant but socially awkward physicists shows them how little they know about life outside of the laboratory.

name: Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 3
p: Still reeling from the loss of Gamora, Peter Quill rallies his team to defend the universe and one of their own - a mission that could mean the end of the Guardians if not successful.

name: Young Sheldon
p: Meet a child genius named Sheldon Cooper (already seen as an adult in The Big Bang Theory (2007)) and his family. Some unique challenges face Sheldon, who is socially impaired.

name: Money Heist
p: An unusual group of robbers attempt to carry out the most perfect robbery in Spanish history - stealing 2.4 billion euros from the Royal Mint of Spain.

name: Thor: Love and Thunder
p: Thor enlists the help of Valkyrie, Korg and ex-girlfriend Jane Foster to fight Gorr the God Butcher, who intends to make the gods extinct.

name: Captain America: The First Avenger
p: Steve Rogers, a rejected military soldier, transforms into Captain America after taking a dose of a 'Super-Soldier serum'. But being Captain America comes at a price as he attempts to take down a warmonger and a terrorist organization.

name: Dolittle
p: A physician who can talk to animals embarks on an adventure to find a legendary island with a young apprentice and a crew of strange pets.
